    "longBusinessSummary": "Vietnam Maritime Commercial Joint Stock Bank provides commercial and retail banking products and services in Vietnam. The company offers card; account; deposits; loans, such as house buying/building, car, consumer, and business loans; insurance; and investment products. It also provides priority banking; corporate banking services, including business solutions; credit; accounts; ebanking; trade finance; cash management; and business incentives. In addition, the company offers mobilizing and receiving short, and medium and long-term deposits; short, medium, and long-term loans to organizations and individuals; foreign exchange transactions; international trade finance services; and discounting of commercial papers, bonds, and other valuable papers. Further, the company provides payment and treasury services; and capital contribution, share purchases, securities investments, and other banking services. Vietnam Maritime Commercial Joint Stock Bank was incorporated in 1991 and is headquartered in Hanoi, Vietnam.",
